{"tid":1639834,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台大明居正教路：緊急法背後目的","createTime":"2019-10-08T17:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:04:49.000Z","uid":103983,"like":71,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"385372ad8b92c3977abf4781f532d79a07c906cc","tid":1639834,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:54:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2IrsjNbs2RE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2IrsjNbs2RE&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=47616e01\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2IrsjNbs2RE</a><br />\n<br />\n晒大家10分鐘時間睇睇佢<br />\n<br />\n簡單講左民選政府難運作，疑點多，要小心中伏<br />\n用緊急法挑起火頭只係第一步<br />\n第二步係引勇武無底線抗爭，搞著埋各國利益，逼人割席<br />\n<br />\n近排吹晒風有舖就燒，狗見後生就拉，又有post 搵到女屍<br />\n呢個明顯係老共手段，火上加油再出宵禁同老解<br />\n<br />\n我同大家一樣興過火屎，但要贏一定要更加冷靜<br />\n只要有底線下遍地開花，針對紅色資本，放學放工幫手文宣<br />\n繼續Be Water，拖長黎玩，黎明一定會到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRDCqW6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRDCqW6.jpg&h=fafedaca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23d45414a8e8420ed6eab1cfae2dd69e70a8e29d","tid":1639834,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:58:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b1f48bfe10be001920044c239a286cd66b088596","tid":1639834,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:59:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be Water</span></span>"},{"pid":"f04a892e5c064ab277c6e325b4521f3872291823","tid":1639834,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f1f4eeb969f140d3cd2dbcc195203865bebf64","tid":1639834,"uid":199553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:06:43.000Z","msg":"明居正講嘢幾中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\